  <h1 style="text-align:center">On Craft</h1>
</header>

<p>I genuinely believe in the craft of opening one heart at a time — through plant medicines and fire ceremonies. I'm really good at this.</p>
      <p>Cannabis and mushrooms — the two I can personally grow. The dream is to have a home where it's legal to cultivate both, and where people come to transform.</p>
      <p>Before that: <em>1 or 2 full-time clients.</em> Traveling together to places where ceremony is legal. Earning from the craft. Building real experience, not waiting for the perfect setup.</p>
      <p>And in parallel — I build. <em>Games, AI, tools.</em> The kind of work that genuinely excites me. The alchemy I've used on myself, I keep for life. The technical side is where I want to create something from scratch and sell it.</p>
      <p>Two fires. Both real.</p>
      <p>If either resonates and you want to work together — reach out. Until then, I build.</p>

